{"tid":643502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信要求終止丁屋政策、認可殯葬區","createTime":"2018-04-26T14:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T06:32:21.000Z","uid":177244,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cead69bd48698400b261101cd1855f6deed025b2","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T14:17:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.landforhongkong.hk/tc/views/views_zone.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landforhongkong.hk%2Ftc%2Fviews%2Fviews_zone.php&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=28fecbf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.landforhongkong.hk/tc/views/views_zone.php</a><br />\n<br />\n專責小組現正進行為期五個月的公眾參與活動，誠邀你考慮各個土地供應選項，並於公眾參與活動期間及於2018年9 月26日或之前，透過以下渠道提出你對各個土地供應選項及相關議題的意見。<br />\n<br />\n專題網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.landforhongkong.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.landforhongkong.hk&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=505d18f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.landforhongkong.hk</a><br />\n郵寄地址<br />\n香港添馬添美道2號<br />\n政府總部西翼17樓<br />\n土地供應專責小組秘書處<br />\n傳真號碼<br />\n2868 4530<br />\n電郵地址<br />\ntfls@devb.gov.hk<br />\n查詢電話<br />\n3509 7737<br />\n專責小組亦將會透過不同方式（包括問卷及電話調查）收集公眾意見，詳情會於本網頁適時公布。<br />\n<br />\n你的參與，你的抉擇，會影響香港土地供應的長遠發展，請踴躍表達你對增闢土地方案的意見。"},{"pid":"89a01046ed3f85470eb9230b910bdfcbedcbb25f","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2FkYUYa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FkYUYa&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ff4403d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2FkYUYa</a><br />\n<br />\n全港市民共用的公私營墳場和火葬場總面積只有八百公頃，政府按一九八三年推出的「山邊殯葬政策」，已經預留了四千公頃﹝即四億平方尺﹞政府土地作為新界原居民的專屬殯葬區，兩者相差五倍。根據民政事務總署資料，過去十年每年批出的「殮葬許可證」不到一千個，假設每個墳墓佔地一千平方尺﹝！﹞，一千公頃土地已經足夠用一百年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/221935_494722611cececdbe6c61458aae3956e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F221935_494722611cececdbe6c61458aae3956e.jpg&h=f9ab9a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/221936_ee173d0f041d34144e75075e72c3d5e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F221936_ee173d0f041d34144e75075e72c3d5e8.jpg&h=ec4314d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去十年，新界區民政事務處每一年批出的殯葬許可證數字如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/221951_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F221951_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=078baf8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據地政總署資料，目前全港共有約五百多個認可殯葬區分佈在新界各區，包括離島、北區、西貢、沙田、大埔、屯門、元朗、荃灣及葵青，其中以元朗區的面積最大，多達一千八百七十一公頃。各分區面積大約如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/222009_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F222009_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=6d3b4907&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7196073dde7ec85c15fe45ccfd511b83e970cf3","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Jux9Pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Jux9Pw&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a27d2ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Jux9Pw</a><br />\n<br />\n截至2012年6月（政府以成本高昂為由，至今仍未更新資料），在全港法定圖則上劃作「鄉村式規劃發展區」的官地面積達1,201.2公頃，扣除不適合發展的268.3公頃（例如道路、斜坡），仍有932.9公頃。雖然這些土地散布在全港各區，未必能簡單地說可以將這900公頃直接用作發展大型社區、解決樓宇供應問題，但若然政府無須預留這批土地作興建丁屋之用，必定可以更靈活地規劃土地用途及鄉郊發展方向。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/222410_ba80d7e012f03253814c86f925fbb789.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F222410_ba80d7e012f03253814c86f925fbb789.jpg&h=d26e92f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3235d0ee9621049dd2877bb220358b55e44540d4","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4469bc78fe0e0ba9f49558bad3da77b6e637583e","tid":643502,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f94e05ccb2c4d5ac4880e9d13dc2fcd29804bfe","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T16:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7eb7ec434f27bed8ec35019e9cd22955b60d786","tid":643502,"uid":26084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"樓主共產鬥地主"},{"pid":"e38fcb7f4eda215983522f6746d02c99a8e0036d","tid":643502,"uid":53577,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T17:07:36.000Z","msg":"唔好嘥氣，基本法列明保障原居民傳統權益。"},{"pid":"58b8e97b798530bb52d5558c8767ff57826e4aff","tid":643502,"uid":100809,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T21:35:42.000Z","msg":"自己買唔到樓 葡萄人地有丁 可以起屋<br />\n魚蛋論 唔要你幫我上樓 要你幫我搞到佢地都冇樓住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 冇丁權"},{"pid":"2d1783b376f25a2654da73491e6b2415da11c632","tid":643502,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7eb7ec434f27bed8ec35019e9cd22955b60d786","tid":643502,"uid":26084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"樓主共產鬥地主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T22:46:03.000Z","msg":"班牛屎佬咁鐘意共產黨，咪俾佢地試吓共產黨當年點鬥死班大地主囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a28efbe6af25024e190e8c73a3ffa8e10a95365","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58b8e97b798530bb52d5558c8767ff57826e4aff","tid":643502,"uid":100809,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T21:35:42.000Z","msg":"自己買唔到樓 葡萄人地有丁 可以起屋<br />\n魚蛋論 唔要你幫我上樓 要你幫我搞到佢地都冇樓住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 冇丁權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:43:29.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n你係咪誤解咗d政策<br />\n宜家係預留一大塊政府地黎延續d所謂傳統習俗"},{"pid":"fc1930c0b7a75986ec8a0621af6ac0edfa25097f","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:44:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Jux9Pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Jux9Pw&d=7rqFycSoXiR%2BlvFX%2B%2FLSDEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a27d2ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Jux9Pw</a> <br />\n<br />\n「認可鄉村範圍」是指環繞某認可鄉村周圍300呎的地方，然而，在全港642條認可鄉村中，有73條鄉村基於各種原因（如地形限制、村民異議等）尚未劃定村界，結果地政總署竟容許這些鄉村的原居民在村外的「鄉村式規劃發展區」興建丁屋，稱為「飛丁」，使丁屋範圍向外擴展，顯然有礙土地規劃。 <br />\n<br />\n建「鄉村擴展區」　公帑補貼丁屋區 <br />\n<br />\n更甚者，在「認可鄉村範圍」內興建丁屋，一般不會動用官地，但「鄉村擴展區」這概念則使法定建屋範圍進佔至官地。鄉村擴展區計劃始於1981年，用來照顧有丁權但無土地的原居民需要，至今完成開發了37個區段、共70公頃的官地，並以私人協約方式批地予原居民，可興建2,000多幢丁屋。2002年，政府認為此計劃牽連太大、成本過高，曾宣布暫緩發展計劃，至於已達後期規劃階段的區段，會按個別情況考慮，研究能否繼續推行。結果，「和宜合鄉村擴展區」在2008年完成開發，「排頭和上禾輋鄉村擴展區」及「蝦尾新村鄉村擴展區」亦已完成收地，預計可在2019年之前完成基建，用來興建丁屋。 <br />\n簡言之，「鄉村擴展區計劃」就是政府動用公帑收地並作開發，然後以優惠價批地予原居民興建丁屋。根據立法會文件，排頭和上禾輋、蝦尾新村，以及其餘八個尚待開發的鄉村擴展區涉地共18.5公頃，原居民絕不能指丁權不影響公共資源分配。<br />\n<br />\n不論是政府文件乃至前鄉議局主席劉皇發的言論，均表明丁屋政策的原意是為了改善新界原居民的居住環境。現時新界已得到妥善發展，若說所有原居民均有賴丁屋政策才能住得舒適，顯然站不住腳。丁屋政策使香港居民分為兩類，一是普通居民，二是新界原居民，他們先天擁有與別不同的權益，包括以折扣價格買地，以及免補地價建屋，成為特權階層，明顯有違現代社會重視的平等價值，更製造了灰色地帶予發展商謀利。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，為確保有合適土地讓原居民興建丁屋，政府需要預留土地，在規劃土地用途時多了一重制肘。如此一來，不管是為了取締特權階層，抑或為了善用土地資源，政府均應思考怎樣在不違反《基本法》的情況下終止丁屋政策。在港人原有生活方式保持50年不變的前提下，林鄭月娥曾提出以2029年為界線，此後出生的原居民不再享有丁權，這無疑是一個可供原居民以至全港市民商議的方案。誠然，此議題會觸動原居民的既得利益，倡議時必定遇上極大阻力，但一個負責任的政府必須擇善固執，展示改革決心，才算盡其應有之義。"},{"pid":"53a4b84669abb4cb67d86668f04079164c7f8d37","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b42c127eae01249ac0d59b7dfc9946bfe5289f","tid":643502,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> G持<br />\n不過林鄭邊夠膽郁班圍村佬"},{"pid":"ca8d8482ac3f3be1439591b5e1d16e921b188c7e","tid":643502,"uid":100809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a28efbe6af25024e190e8c73a3ffa8e10a95365","tid":643502,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58b8e97b798530bb52d5558c8767ff57826e4aff","tid":643502,"uid":100809,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T21:35:42.000Z","msg":"自己買唔到樓 葡萄人地有丁 可以起屋<br />\n魚蛋論 唔要你幫我上樓 要你幫我搞到佢地都冇樓住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 冇丁權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:43:29.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n你係咪誤解咗d政策<br />\n宜家係預留一大塊政府地黎延續d所謂傳統習俗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"哂氣啦 唔通唔留果D地呀 就會用黎起公屋居屋咩<br />\n就算起呀 D鄉村地係哂山卡啦 你會唔會肯住先"},{"pid":"f8811815a0e1b26be2de3b3efa7e335cf1499077","tid":643502,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:32:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}